thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Mark

author: Mark
title: Mark
text: No issues with this service. The last of the 5 packages took much longer to reach it's destination but it was a rural address. It was the only one I hadn't put insurance on so was a little stressed but it got there in the end. Would recommend to use the service. You need to book online though to get the discounted rates.
